data.description: Welcome to this spacious single-family home in Wise, VA, offering a generous 4 bedrooms and 4.5 bathrooms across 7,000 total sq feet. The residence boasts a sturdy full brick exterior, ensuring durability and timeless appeal. Inside, a unique feature awaits—a climate-controlled indoor pool seamlessly integrated into the primary living space. This distinctive addition provides year-round enjoyment, creating a focal point for relaxation and recreation. Nestled on a sprawling 1.3-acre lot, this property is part of the welcoming Wise community. The home's design emphasizes functionality, with large living rooms and generously proportioned bedrooms, ensuring ample living space for your comfort. Step outside onto the multiple outdoor decks, designed on various levels to enhance your outdoor entertaining experience. Take in the breathtaking views of the nearby Appalachian mountains, creating a serene backdrop for gatherings with family and friends.
